title: Ranking Quarterbacks Drafted in the Top Five Since 2010 | Big Board
description:
The Ringer Fantasy Football Show hosts Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly are joined by Nora Princiotti to rank the 15 quarterbacks taken in the top five of the draft since 2010.
Follow ‘The Ringer Fantasy Football Show.’
Hosts: Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly
Guest: Nora Princiotti
